criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18+ years;

          -  Diagnosed as NLUTD;

          -  Incomplete spinal cord injury (SCI), including but not limited to conus medullaris
             syndrome, cauda equina syndrome, etc.;

          -  Radical pelvic surgery: including but not limited to total hysterectomy etc.;

          -  Informed consent signed.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Anatomical bladder outlet obstruction (e.g., prostate enlargement, tumors);

          -  NLUTD induced by stroke, multiple sclerosis, HIV, diabetes mellitus, drug, and
             inflammation or tumor of central nervous system etc.;

          -  Lower urinary tract infections;

          -  Unwillingness to participate.
